Uses of Interface
org.jsonurl.JsonUrlOptions

  • Packages that use JsonUrlOptions 
    Package Description
    org.jsonurl
    This package provides an extensible JSON→URL parser core and static utility methods.
    org.jsonurl.j2se
    This package provides an implementation of the JSON→URL parser based on Java SE datatypes.
    org.jsonurl.jsonorg
    An implementation of the JSON→URL interface based on Douglas Crockford's original Java implementation of JSON.
    org.jsonurl.jsonp
    An implementation of the JSON→URL interface based on the JSON-P interface defined by JSR-374.
